 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学发达了，<span class="_ _4"></span>物质条件好了，<span class="_ _6"></span>也不一定就能带来幸福。<span class="_ _4"></span>爱因斯</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y191 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls22 ws0">坦也说：<span class="_ _8"></span>“单靠知识和技巧，不能<span class="ls19">使人类走上幸福和高尚的</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y174 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">生活。<span class="_ _5"></span>人类有充分的理由，<span class="_ _4"></span>把那些崇高的道德标准和道德价</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y175 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls22 ws0">值的传播者，置于客观真理的发现之上。<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="lse">”古希腊哲学家苏</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y176 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">格拉底<span class="fs4 ls13">（Socrates，前<span class="_ _c"> </span>469—前<span class="_ _c"> </span>399）</span>也主张：<span class="_ _8"></span>“善就是知，知</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y192 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls24 ws0">就是德，德就是福。<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls26">”意思是说，要想获得幸福，其方法是</span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
